---
title: Caramelised Bacon & Mushroom Couscous with Apple & Walnut Salad
description: With umami-packed mushrooms, this colourful Israeli couscous bowl is the perfect midweek pick-me-up! The addition of walnuts, caramelised bacon and a fresh apple salad makes for an easy yet impressive dish.

